## Verdict

T5P narrows the native product blocker: the installed app has the expected
TriggerPoller/handleAgentTrigger surface and the live agent/device prerequisites
are aligned, but native app trigger polling still does not claim fresh target
triggers inside the watchdog window. The full goal remains open.
